# Sidecar files generated by `gazetta dev` and the admin's source-side
# sidecar writer when the Publish panel runs. Shape: `.<8-hex>.hash`,
# `.uses-*`, `.tpl-*` (see docs/sidecars.md). Transient — regenerated
# on every run, never authoritative. Anchored under any `targets/` dir
# so we don't accidentally swallow legitimate dotfiles elsewhere.
**/targets/**/.[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f].hash
**/targets/**/.uses-*
**/targets/**/.tpl-*
